      <p><strong>Capital Preservation:</strong> Purchasing a new excavator at RM650,000 ties up massive capital. A used unit at RM300,000 leaves RM350,000 free for operations, working capital, or acquiring a second machine. In a rising cost environment, cash preservation isn't just smart—it's survival.</p>

