        <li>Hydraulic pressure test</li>
        <li>Undercarriage measurement (track shoe, sprocket, roller wear)</li>
        <li>Structural inspection (boom, stick, bucket cracks)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. Test Drive on Actual Work Site</h3>
